---
import SecctionTitles from "./SecctionTitles.astro";
---


<section id="skills">
    <SecctionTitles title="Skills & Tools" description="Proficencies and Tools to Deliver Exellence" />

    <div class="skills-card">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="" alt="Frontend icon">
            <h6>Frontend</h6>
            <p>
                Proficient in modern frontend technologies including <span>HTML</span>, <span>CSS</span>, 
                <span>JavaScript</span>, and <span>TypeScript</span>, 
                with experience building dynamic and responsive user interfaces. 
                Skilled in creating clean, maintainable, and scalable frontend solutions.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="" alt="Backend Icon">
            <h6>Backend</h6>
            <p>
                Experienced in backend development with a focus on Node.js and <span>TypeScript</span>, 
                leveraging frameworks 
                like <span>Fastify</span> and <span>Express</span> to build efficient APIs and microservices. 
                Additionally, familiar with
                <span>Golang</span> for high-performance backend solutions and proficient in using the 
                <span>Firebase SDK</span> for serverless applications.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="" alt="Database Icon">
            <h6>Database</h6>
            <p>
                Strong knowledge of both relational databases like <span>MariaDB</span> and <span>PostgreSQL</span>, 
                as well as NoSQL databases such as <span>MongoDB</span> and <span>Firestore</span>.
                Skilled in designing scalable and 
                efficient database schemas to support complex application requirements.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="" alt="Frameworks icon">
            <h6>Frameworks & Libraries</h6>
            <p>
                Expertise in using modern libraries and frameworks like <span>React.js</span>, 
                <span>Styled-components</span>,
                and <span>Next.js</span> to create seamless user experiences. Proficient in testing frameworks 
                like <span>Jest</span> for ensuring code quality and robustness.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="" alt="Oher Icons">
            <h6>Other skills</h6>
            <p>
                Well-versed in software architecture principles, including <span>TDD</span>, <span>DDD</span>, 
                and Clean Architecture. 
                Skilled in cloud technologies such as <span>AWS (EC2, S3)</span> and <span>Firebase</span>, 
                as well as CI/CD tools like
                <span>GitHub Actions</span>, <span>Docker</span>. Bilingual with fluency in Spanish (Native) and English (B2).
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<style>
    section {
        margin-top: 10em;
    }

    .skills-card {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;

        margin: 5em 0;
    }

    .card {
        width: 30%;
        min-width: 400px;
        margin: 1em;
        padding: 2em;
        
        display: flex;
        flex-flow: nowrap column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;

        border-radius: 2em;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        background: var(--bg-card);

        h6 {
            margin: 1em 0 1.5em 0;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-accent);
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 420px ){
            min-width: 300px;
        }
    }
</style>